html
  head
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    link(rel="shortcut icon" href='favicon/favicon.ico' type='image/x-icon')
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='css/libs.bundle.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='css/theme.bundle.css')
    title= title
  body
    header.header-bar.mb-3.bg-hero
      .container.d-flex.flex-column.flex-md-row.align-items-center.p-3
        h4.my-0.mr-md-auto.font-weight-normal
          a.text-white(href='/') OurApp
        form.mb-0.pt-2.pt-md-0(action='#' method='POST')
          .row.align-items-center
            .col-md.mr-0.pr-md-0.mb-3.mb-md-0
              input.form-control.form-control-sm.input-dark(name='username' type='text' placeholder='Username' )
            .col-md.mr-0.pr-md-0.mb-3.mb-md-0
              input.form-control.form-control-sm.input-dark(name='password' type='password' placeholder='Password')
            .col-md-auto
              button.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm Sign In
    // header ends here
    .container.py-md-5
      .row.align-items-center
        .col-lg-7.py-3.py-md-5
          h1.display-3 Remember Writing?
          p.lead.text-muted
            | Are you sick of short tweets and impersonal &ldquo;shared&rdquo; posts that are reminiscent of the late 90&rsquo;s email forwards? We believe getting back to actually writing is the key to enjoying the internet again.
        .col-lg-5.pl-lg-5.pb-3.py-lg-5
          form#registration-form(action='/register' method='POST')
            .form-group
              label.text-muted.mb-1(for='username-register')
                small Username
              input#username-register.form-control(name='username' type='text' placeholder='Pick a username' autocomplete='off')
            .form-group
              label.text-muted.mb-1(for='email-register')
                small Email
              input#email-register.form-control(name='email' type='text' placeholder='you@example.com' autocomplete='off')
            .form-group
              label.text-muted.mb-1(for='password-register')
                small Password
              input#password-register.form-control(name='password' type='password' placeholder='Create a password')
            button.py-3.mt-4.btn.btn-lg.btn-success.btn-block(type='submit') Sign up for OurApp
    // footer begins
    footer.border-top.text-center.small.text-muted.py-3
      p.m-0
        | Copyright &copy; 2019
        a.text-muted(href='/') OurApp
        | . All rights reserved.
    script.
      $('[data-toggle="tooltip"]').tooltip()
    script(src='js/vendor.bundle.js')
    script(src='js/theme.bundle.js')
